Keyboard shortcuts

  ↑ ↓ / j k   move selection
  enter       attach alive thread / resume closed thread
  i           focus composer (@ swap profile, enter launch, esc cancel)
  r           quick-reply to the selected alive thread (enter send, esc cancel)
  /           filter by title, repo, branch
  ?           toggle this help
  q / ctrl+c  quit

esc / ? to close